title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum Arena on 1987-12-31
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi DR-2 > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > TLH > FLAC 2448 tagged. Transfer by Andrew F. 06/2012
description:
Set 1

Bertha > Promised Land, Cold Rain & Snow, Little Red Rooster, When Push Comes To Shove, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song > The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Hell In A Bucket, Uncle John's Band > Terrapin Station > Drums > Jam > The Other One > Wharf Rat > Throwing Stones > Not Fade Away

Set 3

Man Smart (Woman Smarter)* > Iko Iko*, Banana Boat Song (Day-O)* > Do You Wanna Dance?*, Knockin' On Heaven's Door

Looters, Neville Brothers, Ramblin' Jack Elliot & David Nelson Had Opening Sets

* - w/ Members Of The Neville Brothers

Commercial Video Release: Ticket To New Year's
